

<div style="width: 75%; margin: auto; background-color: #F1F1F1; border-radius: 20px;">

    <div style="display: flex; background-color: midnightblue; color: white; padding: 0px 15px; border-radius: 20px 20px 0px 0px;">
        <h1>Codeial</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 20px;">
        <p>Hi <%= password.user.name%>!</p>
        <p>Your requested to reset your passwod in Codeial</p>
        <p>Please,click the link below to reset your password</p>
        <p>
            <!-- Because gmail server don't know which server to connect that's why i 
            define full url with access token-->
            <a href="http://localhost:8000/users/new-password?accessToken=<%=password.accessToken%>">Reset Password</a>
        </p>
        <p>Thanks!</p>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px">
        <p>&copy; Codeial.in</p>
        <small>This email was sent to <%= password.user.email%></small><br>
        <small>You recieve the email because you registered with Codeial</small>
    </div> 
    
</div>